死亡是永恆

死	 die; dead; death
亡	 death, destroyed; lose, perish
是	 indeed, yes, right; to be; demonstrative pronoun, this, that
永	 long, perpetual, eternal, forever
恆	 constant, regular, persistent

odnazhdy vy poluchayete znat' smerti
smert' stanet luchshim drugom
tovarishch pozhiznenno
do dnya vy stali sama smert
